    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 11.84,
      "end": 15.68,
      "text": "Recorded by Christine Doer, the known as Assa, Florida.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 17.6,
      "end": 21.34,
      "text": "Asop's Fables, the Lion, and the Three Bulls.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 22.62,
      "end": 28.22,
      "text": "Three Bulls were grazing in a meadow, and were watched by a lion, who longed to capture",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 28.22,
      "end": 33.24,
      "text": "and devour them, but who felt that he was no match for the Three so long as they kept",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 33.24,
      "end": 33.66,
      "text": "together.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 34.78,
      "end": 41.02,
      "text": "So he began by false whispers and malicious hints to format jealousies and distrust among",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 41.02,
      "end": 41.38,
      "text": "them.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 42.22,
      "end": 48.64,
      "text": "This stratagem succeeded so well that Air Longed the Bulls grew cold and unfriendly,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 49.0,
      "end": 53.08,
      "text": "and finally avoided each other and fed each one by himself apart.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 53.98,
      "end": 60.24,
      "text": "No sooner did the lion see this than he fell upon them one by one and killed them in turn.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 61.32,
      "end": 65.26,
      "text": "The Quirals of Friends are the opportunities of those.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 66.72,
      "end": 69.84,
      "text": "End of the Lion and the Three Bulls.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
